Tkx-ROText

This module defines a read-only text widget for Tkx.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

If you don't have Module::Build installed you can fall back to the old 
makefile interface:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Tkx::ROText

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Tkx-ROText

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Tkx-ROText

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Tkx-ROText

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Tkx-ROText

